The paper deals with acquiring and reasoning over commonsense knowledge, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions applications such as chatbots and visual understanding, which are areas of research in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of integer linear programming (ILP) for reasoning suggests a focus on optimization (cs.IR) and algorithms (cs.DB).
